; Regression test for issue #717: Error: Cannot convert a balance with
; multiple commodities to an amount (BZ#717)
;
; When using -H (historical) with mixed commodities and expression-based
; amounts like (2.83/2 EUR), the nail_down function could receive a
; balance with multiple commodities as its market value argument, causing
; a "Cannot convert a balance with multiple commodities to an amount"
; error.  The fix extracts the relevant commodity component from the
; balance for the per-unit cost calculation.

2011-01-01 * Opening balance
    Assets:Investments           1 "BBB" @  2.653329339867 GBP
    Equity:Opening balance

2011-01-10 * Fee
    Liabilities:Credit Card                         -2.83 EUR
    Expenses:Fees                                 (2.83/2 EUR)
    Assets:Receivable

test reg -X EUR -H
11-Jan-01 Opening balance       Assets:Investments            1 BBB        1 BBB
                                Equity:Opening balance GBP-2.653329339867000000000000000000000000000000        1 BBB
                                GBP-2.653329339867000000000000000000000000000000
11-Jan-10 Fee                   Liabilitie:Credit Card    -2.83 EUR        1 BBB
                                                                       -2.83 EUR
                                GBP-2.653329339867000000000000000000000000000000
                                <Adjustment>              -0.01 EUR        1 BBB
                                                                       -2.84 EUR
                                GBP-3.000000000000000000000000000000000000000000
                                Expenses:Fees              1.42 EUR        1 BBB
                                                                       -1.42 EUR
                                GBP-2.653329339867000000000000000000000000000000
                                Assets:Receivable          1.42 EUR        1 BBB
                                GBP-2.653329339867000000000000000000000000000000
end test

test reg -H
11-Jan-01 Opening balance       Assets:Investments             GBP3         GBP3
                                Equity:Opening balance GBP-2.653329339867            0
11-Jan-10 Fee                   Liabilitie:Credit Card    -2.83 EUR    -2.83 EUR
                                <Adjustment>              -0.01 EUR    -2.84 EUR
                                Expenses:Fees              1.42 EUR    -1.42 EUR
                                Assets:Receivable          1.42 EUR            0
end test
